<p>
	Dave and John kick off this week&#39;s show with yet more geekery from your two favorite (and coldest!) geeks. Send in your own questions to get &#39;em answered, or just listen in while John and Dave answer other listeners&#39; questions in a way that teaches you something about your Mac or iOS device, too. There&#39;s always fun to be had and things to learn, and that&#39;s what Mac Geek Gab is here for! Download, press play, and enjoy.</p>
